    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a few imperfections. The exterior has some noticeable dings, paint fading on the hood, and minor scratches throughout. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear, and some of the plastic trim pieces are loose. Mechanically, it runs and drives, though it may soon require attention for minor leaks and routine suspension work. It\u2019s a solid, functional car that has been used regularly but could use some cosmetic TLC.",
