    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. It starts reliably, shifts smoothly, and the engine runs without any known issues, making it a dependable choice for a daily driver. While the interior is clean and the exterior paint retains a nice shine, you may find some minor cosmetic wear and small scratches consistent with careful regular use. Overall, it is a solid, road-ready car that offers great value for someone looking for quality and reliability.",
      "price": 33500.0,
